2013-12-02: version 0.5

 - Fixed a bug in the calendar causing it to highlight a date in the
   future that has the same month and day in month as today.

2011-12-03: version 0.4

 - Added a class for printing menus
 
 - Changed the calendar to not use ansi escapes when printing multiple calendars
 
 - Added shortcuts for creating menus, calendars, tables, and shadowboxes that
   can be mixed in.

2011-10-31: version 0.3

 - Added a class for printing calendars

2011-10-21: version 0.2

 - Fixed bug that caused wrong justification of numeric columns in tables.

2011-10-21: version 0.1

 - Initial release
